  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2-\u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0da7\u0db1\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9f\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0dc0\u0dda\u0d9c\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0d91\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Sami People's Force is also coming to the President-Prime Minister battle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Gayantha Karunathilaka, Member of Parliament of the Sami Jana Balavega, said today (15) afternoon that Sami Jana Balawegaya has decided to run for the post of President and Prime Minister and that the nominations will be handed over next Monday.",
        "Mr. Karunathilaka said that the MPs running for the post of President and Prime Minister will be revealed at the time of handing over the nominations.",
        "Member of Parliament Mr. Gayantha Karunathilaka said this after the discussion held today (15) at the office of the opposition leader in Colombo 7 with the participation of the members of the parliamentary group of the United People's Force."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
